        "width": 1920,
        "height": 1080
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As you can see, the updates have changed the interior, which looks nice and clean with grey cloth upholstery on the bench seat. An aftermarket steering wheel sits on the tilt column, while white-faced Dolphin gauges have been wedged into the factory diamond-shaped cluster, so some of the vintage appeal has been preserved. Vintage Air heat and AC keep the cab nice and comfortable for year-round use, if that’s your pleasure.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
